{
  "stem": "24111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were actually compiling the lists for the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the Jewish-- Israeli-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The JUL was only part of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Ernst worked in the department of the-- it was called the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the earliest transports from Vienna to Theresienstadt-- which was not Auschwitz or it was not the camps in Poland, but was a central holding camp in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The earliest ones were in October of 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He came to me and he says, Bob, your list-- your name came up in one of the lists.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the same evening, or the next morning, I went to Aron-- I didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to Aron Menczer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I say to him, this has happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am losing in a few days my quarters where I have my bed, because my family is going with the Trans-Siberian railway to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have the knowledge to Ernst, my cousin, that my name is in the next list of a transport to Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Aron Menczer at that time had a way of smuggling out Jews out of his group, young Jews, to-- to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About Aron?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of the children coming to him lost their fathers in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By concentration camps, at that time was Dachau and Buchenwald, concentration camps in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were already half orphans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of some of them, the mothers disappeared out of certain reasons I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were full orphans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Aron had now the responsibility of feeding them, giving shelter to them at night and at day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Aron was looking for ways to get those children out of his hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
